Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.32,0:08:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.06,0:08:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.69,0:09:01.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevzdám se
